data.description: Beautiful home in cul-de-sac.  Kitchen updated with new cabinets, granite counters, peninsula for bar stools, stove with built in air fryer, and stone back splash.  Updated electrical circuit box.  New Covered Patio, screened in with electricity and lights, enjoy with no mosquitos.  Additional outside brick patio.  Inside entry way has updated tile, kitchen, eat in kitchen, and den.  Hall Full Bath new tile surrounding the tub.  New Garage Door & Opener,  and  Front Door.  This is a great family home with 3 bedrooms, 2 living areas, 2 1/2 bathrooms. Walking distance to Memorial Junior High School, and Salk Elementary Schools. Easy access to shopping and resturants.
